  "pages": [
    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "Clarence barrow, chief attorney\nIn the Meyer. Haywood and Petit.\nbone cases, left for Rathdrum, Ida,\nno, this morning, accompanied by\nCharles II. Meyer and Mrs. Steve\nAdams. Arrangements are being\nmade for the defense of Steve\nAdams. whose trial on a charge OF\nmurder will soon be taken up, at\nWallace. Idaho. Fred Miller &C.\ncompanied them. The party ex.\npoets TO return tonight."
    }
